re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錦上路</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你 咁多人都飛"},{"pid":"4708fe956707117107dc15aa5c7bc385ccf4dc1e","tid":8151,"uid":13946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:55:59.000Z","msg":"九龍塘，冇次閂一次門就閂到"},{"pid":"883ffdb5d4f3780e8f52a2fd2b6cb67f7c69bdc0","tid":8151,"uid":3255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T08:10:54.000Z","msg":"而家朝早基本上過左天水圍已經爆<br />\n再加埋洪水橋第時朝早基本上應該天水圍打後都唔駛上 天水圍特要加開<br />\n<br />\n如果當年plan定幾個月台<br />\n朝早西鐵應該要咁：<br />\n屯天急行：屯門 兆康 洪水橋 天水圍 美孚 南昌<br />\n元天各停：天水圍 朗屏 元朗 錦上路 荃灣西 美孚 南昌 柯士甸 尖東 紅磡 直通沙中線<br />\n<br />\n屯門去元朗荃灣就天水圍轉各停<br />\n南昌打後基本上有空位 屯門車可以去到嗰度轉<br />\n<br />\n一來屯門落美孚南昌快咗可以增加吸引力<br />\n二來回車快咗增加乘運力"},{"pid":"565a49dfd8fff0f6a66c16980ee3788c5084a6a0","tid":8151,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:28:20.000Z","msg":"金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a716f252a18874f4502c80da696575c14f909396","tid":8151,"uid":10009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>錦上路</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你 咁多人都飛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實應該多人先飛<br />\n咁就可以平衡到 超多人站 vs 正常人流站<br />\n啲人先上到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ebce665f90b0b52ad6d83e15c7acc72f73fcb0","tid":8151,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"大學<br />\n一個鐘淨係一班車停大學都已經夠"},{"pid":"483b370f8a7b2a9d2a8c26ffd6971f5d2064fc20","tid":8151,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39ebce665f90b0b52ad6d83e15c7acc72f73fcb0","tid":8151,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"大學<br />\n一個鐘淨係一班車停大學都已經夠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T09:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a7c9bf123551